\newlabel{fig:user_dist_app}{{17}{15}{Per-user NDCG@10 and Recall@10 score distributions across all test users. KNN-CF and MostPopular show contrasting shapes: MostPopular concentrates scores at a narrow high peak; KNN-CF distributes mass more broadly at lower per-user NDCG but reaches more users}{figure.17}{}}
